{
  "_phone_note": [
    "Phone numbers here are unroutable by construction: Indian mobile numbers start",
    "with 6-9, so a +91 5xxxxxxxxx number can never reach a real handset. That is",
    "deliberate. Seeds get loaded on demo and staging boxes, and from S3 those boxes",
    "may have a live SMS provider configured — a plausible-looking number would send",
    "real OTP texts to a stranger. Real numbers are entered per-hospital via the admin",
    "console (S18), never committed here.",
    "Consequence: seeded staff cannot receive an OTP against a real provider. Local dev",
    "uses SMS_PROVIDER=fake with OTP_DEBUG_ECHO=true, which returns the code in the",
    "response instead."
  ],
